#sexyword don't ya think?? Some might disagree...😵💥
.
Which came first: the literal definition OR the negative connotation we've placed on being "carefree"? 🤔
. . . . 
Thesaurus entries include 'complacent', 'nonchalant', 'indifferent', 'careless' followed by 'easygoing', 'unruffled', serene', 'composed' etc. .
.
It's interesting how worry, stress & anxiety are synonymous with hustle, drive & busy-ness. It's frowned upon, mocked, and even aggravating enough to conjure hate 😡when one is optimistic, steadfast, and trusting of Divine timing. 🙏🏽 When did we fall in love with making ourselves cRaZy?? 😜 When did it become disgraceful in the world of success to be equally happy and simply ok with how the cookie crumbles from time to time? When did being unfettered by worrisome thoughts become blasé? When did 'careless' and 'carefree' become one and the same?? 🤷🏻‍♀️
.
.
Here's to the new generation of Go Getters! To those seeking Joy and trusting Abundance! To those who reap the benefits of ancient tools to discover Self and Truth! To those who KNOW and LET GO! To the #insouciant Souls who don't ever give up and who ROCK THIS WORLD one blithe adventure at a time! #alignedisthenewhustle #lookitup #wordsaremagic #usewisely #knowledgeispower
